              Optimized for Ominix Edge.
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a href="https://huggingface.co/moxin-org/DeepSeek-V3-0324-Moxin-GGUF" target="_blank" class="flex-1 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-text-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-gray-200 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <img src="/images/hf-logo.svg" class="w-4 h-4" alt="HF" />
                Learn More
